cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper is about a new class of Markov decision processes (MDPs) with Tsallis entropy maximization, which generalizes existing maximum entropy reinforcement learning (RL). Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
